thread.title: Air Lease Corporation delivers new Boeing 737-800 to China Airlines

author: eTN Global Editor
title: Air Lease Corporation delivers new Boeing 737-800 to China Airlines
text:
Air Lease Corporation delivers new Boeing 737-800 to China Airlines     
LOS ANGELES, CA - Air Lease Corporation announced the delivery of one new Boeing 737-800NG to China Airlines (Taiwan), the first of three new Boeing 737-800 aircraft deliveries on long-term lease from ALC’s order book with Boeing. The second 737-800 is scheduled to deliver in fall 2015, and the third in spring 2016. 
“We are very pleased to announce this first of three new 737-800 aircraft delivering to China Airlines, and look forward to continuing our successful relationship with their management team as the airline renews and modernizes its fleet,” said John Plueger, President and Chief Operating Officer of Air Lease Corporation.
